INSTALL

* Linux:
	$ make install (This will run the distutils install target with sudo.)
	note: This *could* overwrite any exisiting /etc/evanescent.yaml.conf
	file that you have, so backup your old one beforehand please.

* Other Operating Systems:
	Currently not supported. Most code is cross platform. Patches accepted.


DEPENDENCIES

* python-utmp - for working with utmp
* python-yaml - for config file parsing
* python-notify - for libnotify notifications
* python-cheetah - for man page generation from templates
* jhelp - for various helper libraries
* libxss-dev - for building x idle detection code

